<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Earnest1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Earnest,</orth> subst., handsel, a part paid beforehand as a pledge: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.659" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 659</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 47</bibl> <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 49</bibl>. Quibbling in <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.163" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 1, 163</bibl> and <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 24</bibl>. Followed by <cit><quote>of:</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2.169" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 169</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 104</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.5.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 5, 65</bibl>. <cit><quote>in e.:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 42</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 1, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 16</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>